name: Rachel Ponce
description: Hello! My name is Rachel Ponce, and I am a Computer Science Engineering student at the University of Florida. For as long as I can remember, my actions have always been influenced by my genuine love for learning and my enthusiasm for trying new things. I am passionate about software engineering because of its countless interdisciplinary applications, its ability to better the lives of individuals using everyday technology, and the opportunity it presents to redefine what is possible.
